OL,3,CMeet some of the first barbers in the
OL,4,Ccountry training to spot men in
OL,5,Cdistress
OL,7,FBarbers in Swindon are being trained
OL,8,Fto spot signs of distress in their
OL,9,Fclients as part of a new initiative
OL,10,Ftackling a growing male mental health
OL,11,Fcrisis.
OL,13,FStaff at Supreme Barbers in the town
OL,14,Fcentre are the first in the region to
OL,15,Fsign up to a scheme like this, ran by
OL,16,Fmental health professionals working
OL,17,Ffor Swindon Borough Council.
OL,19,FIt's hoped it will expand, empowering
OL,20,Fmen across the town, and beyond, to
OL,21,Fask for help.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
