OL,3,CMeet some of the first barbers in the
OL,4,Ccountry training to spot men in
OL,5,Cdistress
OL,7,FBarber Danny Hegarty told ITV West
OL,8,FCountry a haircut often opens up
OL,9,Fdeeper conversation.
OL,11,FHe said: "I've been cutting hair for
OL,12,Fover 26 years.
OL,14,F"The amount of people who've been at
OL,15,Fbreaking point and we've had a chat
OL,16,Fand I've found out afterwards that
OL,17,Fchat has helped somebody in not going
OL,18,Fahead and maybe self-harming, possibly
OL,19,Fworse.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
