OL,3,CMeet some of the first barbers in the
OL,4,Ccountry training to spot men in
OL,5,Cdistress
OL,7,F"I've had first-hand experience of
OL,8,Fpeople saying that to me you know."
OL,10,FLucas Santiago, the owner of Supreme
OL,11,FBarbers, said: "We have customers talk
OL,12,Fabout their life to us. Sometimes
OL,13,Fthey're not feeling good and they have
OL,14,Fa lot of things going on through their
OL,15,Flife.
OL,17,F"They need someone to talk about that.
OL,18,FIt makes a huge difference to have
OL,19,Fsomeone to listen to what you have to
OL,20,Fsay."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
