OL,3,CMeet some of the first barbers in the
OL,4,Ccountry training to spot men in
OL,5,Cdistress
OL,7,FWith years of experience listening to
OL,8,Fpeople's problems, staff at Supreme
OL,9,FBarbers are now going to be given
OL,10,Fprofessional mental health training to
OL,11,Fhelp spot the signs of someone in need.
OL,13,FThe initiative is believed to be the
OL,14,Ffirst of its kind in the South West.
OL,16,FCouncillor Jim Grant of Swindon
OL,17,FBorough Council said: "If we can train
OL,18,Fthe barbers to understand what people
OL,19,Fare saying, then they can signpost
OL,20,Fthem on to mental health professionals.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
