OL,3,CMeet some of the first barbers in the
OL,4,Ccountry training to spot men in
OL,5,Cdistress
OL,7,F"This is a real great initiative for
OL,8,FSwindon and I'm really hoping lots of
OL,9,Fbarbershops can get on board so we can
OL,10,Freally make a difference."
OL,12,FFor one of the barbers at Supreme,
OL,13,Fit's a subject close to home. Marcus
OL,14,FBatista lost a close friend to suicide.
OL,16,FHe said: "I lost one of my friends
OL,17,Flast year, same age as me, to suicide.
OL,18,FSo I thought it would be a really
OL,19,Fgreat thing to do. It's something to,
OL,20,Fyou know, give back and try and make
OL,21,Fthis not happen again."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
