OL,4,Ccountry training to spot men in
OL,5,Cdistress
OL,7,FBarber Paul Miller added: "It's just
OL,8,Fnice to support those who are
OL,9,Fstruggling and you want people like
OL,10,Fthat to come into the barbers and
OL,11,Frelax and talk to you.
OL,13,F"We're just there to help people and
OL,14,Fwant people to know we are here."
